# Codex mirror (dustin-thomason)

**`AGENTS.md` is generated output only.** **Never edit `AGENTS.md` directly.** All behavioral changes **must** be made in the source `.mdc` files under `.cursor/rules/`; the regeneration script **overwrites** any direct edits to `AGENTS.md`.

When you **create or edit** any file under `.cursor/rules/` or `.cursor/skills/` in this repo:

1. Run **`.\scripts\sync-agents-md.ps1`** from the `dustin-thomason` repo root before you finish.
2. If `AGENTS.md` changed, stage it with the same work (do not leave the mirror stale).

```
Good: edit .cursor/rules/<rule>.mdc, then run .\scripts\sync-agents-md.ps1 to regenerate AGENTS.md.
Bad:  hand-editing AGENTS.md (the next sync silently overwrites it).
```
